<h2><a name="status"/>Status of the Installation Guide</h2>

<p>

A large part of the Guide was copied from the old installation guide for Woody.
Some parts still need to be updated and some parts should to be restructured
and/or rewritten to improve readability.<br/>
The main parts that need to be updated are chapters 2 to 5.

</p><p>

The second concern is that the information for some architectures is outdated
and/or not reviewed for Debian Installer. This is indicated by a warning at
the beginning of the manual.

</p>

